    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (((tmp + 0.76 + tmp + 0.69) * v2) - v0)
    v2 = (v2 / v1)
    v0 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.01) - (v0 + 0.85 / v0 + 0.90)) - wp.cos((v0 + 0.19 + v2 + 0.09)))
    tmp = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.78) * (v0 + 0.63 - v0 + 0.69)) - (v2 - (tmp + 0.95 / v2 + 0.87)))
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.abs(wp.sin(tmp + 0.33)))
    data[tid] = v0
